Then, make your `ImageCardView` extend `MaterialCardView` instead of `BaseCardView`, and add the following code in it:

```kotlin
init {
	borderWidth = 0f
	setBorderColor(Color.WHITE)
}

override fun setSelected(selected: Boolean) {
	super.setSelected(selected)
	borderWidth = if (selected) 4f else 0f
}
