One solution could be to use SAP Cloud SDK for this. As Cloud SDK provide support for both Neo and CF. With SDK you can achieve the above as follows:

For tenant on CF:

	TenantAccessor.executeWithTenant( new ScpCfTenant( &quot;tenantname&quot;, &quot;tenant.domain&quot;),() -&gt; {
        TenantAccessor.getCurrentTenant().getTenantId();
    });


For tenant on Neo:

    TenantAccessor.executeWithTenant( new ScpNeoTenant(tenantContext), () -&gt; {
        TenantAccessor.getCurrentTenant().getTenantId();
    });


Where the lambda expression is the callable method on the tenant.

I hope this works for you.

